headline: Barclays Raises AutoZone (AZO) PT to $4,510 on Anticipation of Higher Earnings
summary: AutoZone Inc. (NYSE:AZO) is one of the stocks to invest in before they split next. On September 11, Barclays analyst Seth Sigman raised the firm’s price target on AutoZone to $4,510 from $3,916, while keeping an Overweight rating on the shares as part of a FQ4 2025 earnings preview.
